Privacy Policy

AquaTrack respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how your information is handled within the app.

Data Collection

AquaTrack does not collect, store, or share any personal data such as name, email address, location, or device identifiers.

Health Data

All water intake data is stored locally on your device only. This data is never sent to any server or third party.

